column1: https://homestars.com/on/martintown/design-project-management,1,https://homestars.com/on/martintown/design-project-management,Design/Project Management,2801479,NA,/companies/2801479-dimartinodesigns?searched_category_id=456&service_area=1866348,"Di Martino Designs was born thirteen years ago with one goal: architecture is art you can walk through. Since then, we have focused our zeal for design and suppliers into the contemporary house designs.  Di Martino Designs is a design and project management company serving the general public, engineers, contractors and developers.
Designer Paul Di Martino, personally designs each home and flawlessly sculpts the architecture, landscapes and interiors into homes that are anything but ordinary.

We partner with some of the finest engineers, contractors and architects to craft a high quality design and building plan for small or large scale projects. Di Martino Designs is devoted to providing exceptional services to our clients, competitive rates, turn-key services and single point of contact for all their needs.

column2: Design-build of houses, new structures, additions and                 renovations

column1: All of our members possess Provincial Mechanical & Structural Licensing with advance design and project management education as well as, polished industry experience. This strong combination allows us to provide the most accurate and efficient services to our clients. Paul Di Martino creates thoughtful and copious details and timeless materials.
